					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td valign="top" class="tablefloating" colspan="2">Room 406AB&nbsp;</td>
					</tr>
					<tr>
						<td valign="top" class="tablefloating" colspan="2">An E<sup>3</sup> tradition, Sneak Peeks gives attendees an exclusive look at three games still in development: Learn how the pros manage the game development process--how they juggle the needs of their team, their publisher, and the media. Sneak Peeks is designed to inform by presenting a unique window into the game development process, so come prepared to take notes, ask questions, and learn how the top designers and project managers handle the pressures of developing AAA product--then use that knowledge to make your own game development process more efficient and more productive.&nbsp;</td>
